Package: distroviz
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Statistical Distribution Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Vincent", "Biot", email = "vincent@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create interactive statistical visualizations including box plots,
    violin plots, and density plots using D3.js. Supports single sample and
    comparative visualizations with outlier detection and customizable reference lines.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    htmlwidgets (>= 1.5.0),
    htmltools
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
URL: https://github.com/vincentbiot/distroviz_r
BugReports: https://github.com/vincentbiot/distroviz_r/issues
